The paper discusses the definition of AI in terms of multi-agent systems, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also touches upon machine learning (cs.LG), control systems (cs.SY), and robotics (cs.RO) as these fields are closely related to the development of AI systems.
